{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"728","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"英運輸部擬徵「網購送貨稅」降低環境污染","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>17:53 2020/06/29 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>中時 施施</span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;<img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E7%B6%B2%E8%B3%BC%E7%A8%85.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 534px;' /></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>英國《泰晤士報》<span lang='EN-US'>29</span>日報導，運輸部科學諮詢委員會本月建議，向所有網購消費者強制徵收類似塑膠袋稅的費用，以緩解網購送貨激增導致的污染。上述措施將讓消費者在訂購或退貨時更加慎重，或轉向實體商店購買。<span lang='EN-US'>(</span>美聯<span lang='EN-US'>)</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>英國《泰晤士報》<span lang='EN-US'>29</span>日報導，運輸部科學諮詢委員會本月提交<span lang='EN-US'>1</span>份報告，建議向所有網購消費者強制徵收類似塑膠袋稅的費用，以緩解網購送貨激增導致的污染。運輸部表示會考慮建議，未來可能展開公眾諮詢。目前尚不清楚收費細節及相關可能的影響。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報告指，免費送貨或退貨服務，導致消費者網購量大增。以<span lang='EN-US'>2018</span>年<span lang='EN-US'>12</span>月「黑色星期五」及感恩節長假的活動為例，退貨總額達<span lang='EN-US'>24</span>億英鎊。報告敦促，運輸部可透過「將送貨和退貨的真實成本轉嫁給客戶，以減少不必要的過度訂購」，並讓消費者認識網購的負面影響，同時鼓勵持續性網購。有評論指，上述措施將讓消費者在訂購或退貨時更加慎重，或轉向實體商店。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>運輸部最新數據顯示，貨車的氮氧化物排放量在<span lang='EN-US'>2007</span>年至<span lang='EN-US'>2017</span>年間，大幅飆升了<span lang='EN-US'>43%</span>，至<span lang='EN-US'>9.93</span>萬噸；截至今年<span lang='EN-US'>3</span>月底，包括貨車在內的輕型商用車在英國共累計行駛<span lang='EN-US'>811</span>億公里，比<span lang='EN-US'>10</span>年前增長<span lang='EN-US'>24%</span>。網購巨人亞馬遜等近年轉用機器及小型自駕車等送貨。</span><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>(</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>中時<span lang='EN-US'> )</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200629004230-260408?chdtv</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-07-02","clk_count":"157"}},"__N_SSG":true}